# Test Tree Photos

Real tree photos from iNaturalist (CC-licensed open data) for pipeline integration testing.

## Species (common Austin street trees)

| Prefix | Species | Scientific |
|--------|---------|------------|
| liveoak_ | Plateau Live Oak | Quercus fusiformis |
| cedarelm_ | Cedar Elm | Ulmus crassifolia |
| pecan_ | Pecan | Carya illinoinensis |
| baldcypress_ | Bald Cypress | Taxodium distichum |
| oak_bark_ | Oak bark close-ups | Quercus spp. |

## Photo Types

- `*_angle1`, `*_angle2`: Full tree views from different angles
- `*_0_0`, `*_0_1`: Multiple photos per observation (first number = observation, second = photo index)
- `oak_bark_*`: Bark close-up photos

## Source

Downloaded from iNaturalist research-grade observations near Austin, TX.
Photos are CC-licensed via iNaturalist open data S3 bucket.
